name: Blessed by the Fountain
description: As many of you, my HEN adventure begins thanks to the Tezos Fountain. Without it I wouldn't be able to start, so i just wanted to say thanks. 33 editions, one for each cent they gave me. If you decide to grab one, let me know and i'll send you the full res image with no text overlay so you can use it as you wish. IG @lucas.spataro Minted 16.04.21
